metadata.name: Dr. Eams
metadata.description:
Reality is a dream portal. We go from one portal to another, entering a different dream each time we close our eyes. 

Somewhere in a hidden lab on Doodverse, there lives a mysterious Dr. Eams â€“ architect of dreams and conjured memories. Join Dr. Eams on an expedition to the deepest parts in our subconscious. In here you will discover your alternate realities, memories; of which they are possibly conjured, stolen or reimagined fragments of our past and future. Till when do these dreams end, no one knows. Find yours today.
